events.name: Li-ion battery supply chain expansion
events.wd_description: The industry that manufactures Li-ion batteries is expected to grow as much as ten times its current size, and the supply chain that feeds the materials into that industry also has to expand at a similar rate.

events.name: Cobalt shipment increase
events.wd_description: The total amount of cobalt shipments is not very flexible, with most being mined in the Democratic Republic of Congo, primarily as a co-extracted mineral.
